==製作==
在2012年5月19日，[[西蒙·柏奇|西蒙·柏奇]]則飾演為赫克托<ref name=Simon>{{cite news|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|title=Simon Pegg On A ‘Search For Happiness’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/simon-pegg-on-a-search-for-happiness/|accessdate=9 February 2014|newspaper=deadline.com|date=19 May 2012|archive-date=2014-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140731053213/http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/simon-pegg-on-a-search-for-happiness/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2012年9月6日，[[羅莎蒙·派克|羅莎蒙·派克]]和[[克里斯托弗·普卢默|克里斯托弗·普卢默]]，分別演克萊雅和歌爾曼教授。2012年11月1日，[[斯特兰·斯卡斯加德|斯特兰·斯卡斯加德]]也參演為艾德華<ref name=Stellan>{{cite news|last=Foreman|first=Liza|title=Stellan Skarsgård Joins 'Hector and the Search for Happiness'|url=http://www.thewrap.com/awards/column-post/stellan-skarsgard-joins-hector-and-search-happiness-63291|accessdate=10 February 2014|newspaper=thewrap.com|date=1 November 2012}}</ref>，德國女星[[維羅尼卡·費瑞爾|威雷妮卡．法雷斯]]也參與演出，她飾演為安嘉莉<ref name="imdb">{{Cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1626146/fullcredits?ref_=tt_ov_st_sm |title=IMDb Entry |access-date=2014-11-24 |archive-date=2017-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101140329/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1626146/fullcredits?ref_=tt_ov_st_sm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該片在2013年1月開始<ref name=Rosamund-Christopher>{{cite news|last=Siegel|first=Tatiana|title=Rosamund Pike and Christopher Plummer Cast in 'Hector and the Search for Happiness'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/rosamund-pike-christopher-plummer-hector-search-for-happiness-368428|accessdate=10 February 2014|newspaper=hollywoodreporter.com|date=6 September 2012|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206094018/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/rosamund-pike-christopher-plummer-hector-search-for-happiness-368428|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其後在2013年4月2日，[[東妮·克莉蒂|東妮·克莉蒂]]和[[尚·連奴|尚·連奴]]也參與演出<ref name=Toni-Jean>{{cite news|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|title=Toni Collette, Jean Reno Set To Star In ‘Hector And The Search For Happiness’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/toni-collette-jean-reno-set-to-star-in-hector-and-the-search-for-happiness/|accessdate=10 February 2014|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2 April 2013|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714152224/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/toni-collette-jean-reno-set-to-star-in-hector-and-the-search-for-happiness/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本片製作費用預算達至900萬英鎊（1500萬美元）<ref name="womeninfilm.ca"/>。

2014年9月19日，[[相对论传媒|相对论传媒]]承包[[美國|美國]]分銷電影所有版權<ref name=Relativity>{{cite news|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|title=Relativity Acquires U.S. On ‘Hector And The Search For Happiness’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/relativity-acquires-u-s-on-hector-and-the-search-for-happiness/|accessdate=23 April 2014|newspaper=deadline.com|date=22 April 2014|archive-date=2014-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620181544/http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/relativity-acquires-u-s-on-hector-and-the-search-for-happiness/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==放映==
